sources.title: Atomic Rulers (1965) STARMAN
sources.description:
Stars: Ken Utsui, Junko Ikeuchi, Shôji Nakayama 
 Directors: Koreyoshi Akasaka, Teruo Ishii

 Super criminals are planning to infiltrate Earth with mass nuclear destruction! Only Starman can defend civilization by thwarting evil!
